The following transcript of a telephone conversation that occurred on 07/03/2049 between Undersecretary General D.C. Al Fine and President Dan Crenshaw, conducted via the direct hotline, is strictly classified and available only to the selected personnel of the High Command. Proliferation of the below file is strictly forbidden.
