[[div class="blockquote"]]
[[=image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/lte-1998-burnout-blaecca-parallax/highcommand.png height="100px"]]
= **[[size larger]]##102141|Office of the Undersecretary-General##[[/size]]**
